{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place clams in salt water to open them up (approx. 30 minutes). Meanwhile, peel prawns, reserving shells and heads.","Place 800 g water and reserved shells and heads in mixing bowl. Rinse and drain clams then place in Varoma dish. Place covered Varoma into position and steam <b>14 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Set covered Varoma aside and keep warm. Drain stock through a fine sieve into a jug and set aside. Rinse mixing bowl.","Place garlic, tomatoes, red peppers, green peppers and oil in mixing bowl, chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b> then sauté <b>10 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add wine and, without measuring cup, cook <b>2 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 1<b>.","Add 1 Tbsp parsley, saffron, salt, rice, orange juice and 1000 g reserved stock then cook <b>15 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b>.","Add reserved peeled prawns and stir in with spatula. Place steamed clams in a serving dish. Pour over rice and stir a little with spatula. Garnish with remaining 1 Tbsp parsley and serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["400 g fresh clams, cleaned","800 g water, plus extra for clams","1 - 2 tsp salt, to taste, plus extra for clams","300 g raw prawns, unpeeled","2 garlic cloves","200 g tinned chopped tomatoes","150 g red peppers, cut in pieces","150 g green peppers, cut in pieces","70 g olive oil","150 g white wine","2 Tbsp fresh parsley leaves, roughly chopped","1 pinch saffron","350 g short grain rice (e.g. paella rice) (see tip)","50 g orange juice, freshly squeezed"]}],"id":"r396222","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-NO_8P7sfd2g\/XZM0d44tjqI\/AAAAAAAAa88\/7la-xoFrR9cIoLzM8KX8bpTjlW00WDDRgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_zH4dj0a9mr7KNzxf.png","title":"Seafood Rice","publishedAt":"2018-09-03T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"25 g","fat":"15 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"53 g","calories":"1920 kJ \/ 459 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving dish, fine sieve, jug","hintsAndTricks":["If paella rice is not available, substitute with another short grain rice such as risotto rice."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","1h 15m","6 portions"]}